<topic id="ditamap-run-dita-ot-integrator">
  <title>Integrate/Install DITA-OT Plugins Transformation</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Transformation Scenarios<indexterm>Integrate DITA-OT
          plugins</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Integrate DITA-OT plugins</indexterm>
        <indexterm>Install DITA-OT plugins</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_wbl_cgk_54b"><ph keyref="product"/> comes bundled with a transformation scenario
      designed to integrate DITA-OT <xref keyref="glossentry_plugin">plugins</xref>. These DITA-OT
        <term>plugins</term> are used for various customizations. It is called <b>Integrate/Install
        DITA-OT Plugins</b> and is found in the <uicontrol>DITA Map</uicontrol> section of the <xref
        href="configure-transformation-dialog.dita#configure-transformation-dialog"
            ><uicontrol><image href="../img/TransformConfig16.png"/>Configure Transformation
          Scenario(s)</uicontrol> dialog box</xref>.<note type="attention" id="note_xbl_cgk_54b">The
        integration will be performed on the DITA-OT version specified in the <xref
          href="preferences-dita.dita#preferences-dita/DITA-OT-section"><uicontrol>DITA Open
            Toolkit</uicontrol> section of the <uicontrol>DITA</uicontrol> preferences
        page</xref>.</note><note conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/note-custom-dita-ot-limitations"
        id="note_njq_b4z_ctb"/></p>
    <section id="creating_the_transformation_scenario">
      <title>Running the Transformation Scenario</title>
      <p id="p_ybl_cgk_54b">To integrate a DITA-OT <term>plugin</term>, follow these steps:<ol id="ol_zbl_cgk_54b">
          <li id="li_acl_cgk_54b" irina="irina">If <ph keyref="product"/> was installed in the default location, you may need to
            restart and run it as an administrator.</li>
          <li id="li_bcl_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Select the <uicontrol><image href="../img/ApplyStyleSheet16.png"/>Apply Transformation
              Scenario(s)</uicontrol> or <xref
              href="configure-transformation-dialog.dita#configure-transformation-dialog"
                  ><uicontrol><image href="../img/TransformConfig16.png"/>Configure Transformation
                Scenario(s)</uicontrol></xref> action from the <uicontrol>DITA Maps
              Manager</uicontrol> toolbar (you could also use the same action on the main toolbar or
            open the <xref href="scenarios-view.dita#scenarios-view"><b>Transformation Scenarios</b>
              view</xref>).</li>
          <li id="li_ccl_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Select the <b>Integrate/Install DITA-OT Plugins</b> transformation
            scenario. If the <i>integrator</i> is not visible, select the <b>Show all scenarios</b>
            action that is available in the <uicontrol><image href="../img/Settings16.png"
                id="image_km5_xrs_yq"/>Settings</uicontrol> drop-down menu.</li>
          <li id="li_dcl_cgk_54b" irina="irina"><xref href="apply-transformation-scenarios.dita#apply-transformation-scenarios">Apply
              the scenario</xref>.</li>
          <li id="li_ecl_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Check the <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol> panel at the bottom of the application to
            make sure the build was successful.</li>
          <li id="li_fcl_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Restart <ph keyref="product"/> with your normal permissions.</li>
        </ol></p>
    </section>
